00:03:35.210 --> 00:03:37.510
Is that all that we'll
ever do with them?

00:03:37.510 --> 00:03:41.110
Is entertainment the sum total
of what this powerful medium

00:03:41.110 --> 00:03:42.540
is capable of accomplishing?

00:03:42.540 --> 00:03:44.380
And don't get me wrong, I
think entertainment is

00:03:44.380 --> 00:03:45.770
important and meaningful
