00:03:45.770 --> 00:03:47.910
It does not need another
purpose to be

00:03:47.910 --> 00:03:49.590
important to society.

00:03:49.590 --> 00:03:51.760
But I thought to myself,
we could do more.

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:52.690
And so I started to research.

00:03:52.690 --> 00:03:53.870
I started to play around.

00:03:53.870 --> 00:03:55.030
I started to build apps.

00:03:55.030 --> 00:03:57.750
And out of that came my first
book, "game-based marketing,"

00:03:57.750 --> 00:04:01.090
which came out in 2010 and
was followed up by the

00:04:01.090 --> 00:04:04.900
