I wrote for O'Reilly.

00:04:04.900 --> 00:04:07.520
And then now, my new book, "The
Gamification Revolution."

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:11.710
And so for the last, however
many years, about seven years,

00:04:11.710 --> 00:04:14.640
I spent my life devoted to this
topic of how to use games

00:04:14.640 --> 00:04:18.260
to change people's behavior,
change the world.

00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:21.529
I now also edit the site,
gamification.co, which is the

00:04:21.529 --> 00:04:23.780
main site that covers
